snippet.title: Yupitergrad: Next Challenges | Update Trailer
snippet.description:
Komrades, Next Challenges update featuring ten brand new levels in Time Attack mode will be waiting for you from May 20, 2021. Be careful, though, because you'll encounter new obstacles and traps as you navigate the winding corridors! We also added a 120Hz refresh rate for Oculus Quest 2 goggles, new music and fixes some minor issues. The update is free, and available on Viveport, Steam and Oculus stores. 
Next Challenges will come to PlayStation VR shortly after.

***
Yupitergrad is also available on:

Oculus Quest: https://www.oculus.com/experiences/quest/3622969487764448/
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1352020/Yupitergrad/
Viveport: https://www.viveport.com/90052cfc-f3da-4052-abd8-c182f6f9b99a
Oculus Rift: https://www.oculus.com/experiences/rift/2521589964574061/
PlayStation Store: https://store.playstation.com/en-us/product/UP4818-CUSA24780_00-8493795692944248
